&lt;p&gt;    fix a bug in windows&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The `SOCKET` type is defined as a unsigned number in windows, the &lt;br/&gt;
`evutil_socket_t` variables are always large than zero, therefore the condition &lt;br/&gt;
not work well here.&lt;/p&gt;

